---
layout: default.hbs
subject: Reset Your Password
---
<span class="preheader">You're receiving this email because you requested a password reset</span>
<table class="header" align="center"  width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#FDFDFE"  border="0">
    <tr>
        <td class="wrapper border-bottom" valign="middle">
            <a href="{{WEB_URL}}"><img class="logo" border="0" src="{{default.WEB_URL}}/nkba-logo@2x.png" alt="NKBA" height="30" width="141"></a>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
<table class="main" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
    <tr>
        <td class="wrapper">
            <table width="100%">
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block pt1" valign="top">
                        <h1>Reset your password</h1>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4" valign="top">
                        \{{name}},
                    </td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4" valign="top">
                        You're receiving this email because you requested a password reset from the <a href="\{{WEB_URL}}">NKBA</a>.<br/>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4">
                        <a href="\{{WEB_URL}}/reset/\{{token}}">Click here to reset your password.</a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4">
                        If you did not make this request, please notify us at <a href="mailto:cloud@nkba.org">cloud@nkba.org</a>.
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
<div class="footer">
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td class="align-center">
                This message was sent to <a href="mailto:\{{email}}">\{{email}}</a> at your request.<br/> The National Kitchen
                and Bath Association<br/> 687 Willow Grove St<br/> Hackettstown, NJ 07840
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>